breakingChangesNotes: The following output context paths of the ***core-get-cases*** command have been removed and are now retrievable using the **get-enriched-case-data** argument set to true (under the Core.Case.CaseExtraData prefix): **Core.Case.notes**, **Core.Case.detection_time**, **Core.Case.xdr_url**, **Core.Case.manual_description**, **Core.Case.starred_manually**.
